headline: ADP Announces Pricing of its Senior Notes Due 2032
summary: ADP (Nasdaq: ADP), a leading global technology company providing comprehensive cloud-based human capital management (HCM) solutions, yesterday announced the pricing of a public offering of $1.0 billion aggregate principal amount of its 4.750% senior notes due 2032.
